## Folder Structure

```
{project}/
├── knowledge/                ← Tycono world. AI agent's cwd. Git root.
│   ├── CLAUDE.md             ← Only AI entry point
│   ├── .claude/skills/       ← Role skill guides
│   │   ├── _shared/
│   │   └── {role-id}/SKILL.md
│   ├── roles/
│   │   ├── roles.md          ← Hub
│   │   └── {role-id}/
│   │       ├── role.yaml
│   │       ├── profile.md
│   │       └── journal/
│   ├── architecture/         ← Hub (technical architecture)
